release_note: Hi velocity lovers! We re excited to announce a new feature: PhotoVelo! You can now animate your photos and sync them to your beat. Photovelo is like velocity templates but for it is your photos this time! Enjoy! Feel free to reach us from Instagram velomingoapp or Tiktok velomingoapp.

Hi velocity lovers! We re excited to announce a new feature: Velocity Animations. You can now add velocity shakes anywhere in your videos. Just press and hold the animation button and there it is! Velocity animation settings also allow you to create velocity shakes synched to video beats. Enjoy! Feel free to reach us from Instagram velomingoapp or Tiktok velomingoapp.
